TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Your commander is a strong unit and can also build many things. In this tutorial your commander is surrounded by 'ghost' units - build these on the spots indicated and follow the instructions to make yourself a base. Begin by selecting your commander and right clicking to move him.

TriggerLogic.Text: The grey spots on the ground are metal spots.
You can build metal extractors on them to increase your metal income.
There are two ways to make energy - solar and wind. Build a solar collector here
The other resource you'll need is energy.
To make units, you'll need a lab. Make a kbot lab here.
You'll need radar to find out where your enemy is. Build one here.

TriggerLogic.Message: Well done! To complete this mission, use your lab to build some units and then destroy the deserted enemy base on top of the central hill. Build mexes on a few nearby metal spots so as you have enough resources to use your lab. You only need one mex per spot. Build more solars/wind generators if you find you're short of energy.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Your commander can help your lab build faster. Select your com and right click on your lab to guard it.
